{"word":"Diligence","slug":"diligence","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Diligence</b> Jesus an example of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=35'>Mar 1:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=49'>Luk 2:49</a><br/> Required by God in:<br/> - Seeking Him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=22&verse=19'>1Ch 22:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=6'>Heb 11:6</a> <br/> - Obeying Him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=6&verse=17'>Deu 6:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=11&verse=13'>Deu 11:13</a> <br/> - Hearkening to Him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=55&verse=2'>Isa 55:2</a> <br/> - Striving after perfection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=3&verse=14'>Phi 3:14</a> <br/> - Cultivating Christian graces<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=1&verse=5'>2Pe 1:5</a> <br/> - Keeping the soul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=9'>Deu 4:9</a> <br/> - Keeping the heart<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=4&verse=23'>Pro 4:23</a> <br/> - Labors of love<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=6&verse=12'>Heb 6:12</a> <br/> - Following every good work<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=3&verse=10'>1Ti 3:10</a> <br/> - Guarding against defilement<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=15'>Heb 12:15</a> <br/> - Seeking to be found spotless<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=3&verse=14'>2Pe 3:14</a> <br/> - Making our calling sure<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=1&verse=10'>2Pe 1:10</a> <br/> - Self-examination<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=77&verse=6'>Psa 77:6</a> <br/> - Lawful business<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=27&verse=23'>Pro 27:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=9&verse=10'>Ecc 9:10</a> <br/> - Teaching religion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=2'>2Ti 4:2</a>; <a href='B:'></a> <br/> - Instructing children<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=6&verse=7'>Deu 6:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=11&verse=19'>Deu 11:19</a> <br/> - Discharging official duties<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=19&verse=18'>Deu 19:18</a> <br/> Saints should abound in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=8&verse=7'>2Co 8:7</a><br/> Required in the service of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=9&verse=4'>Joh 9:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=6&verse=9'>Gal 6:9</a><br/> Is not in vain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=58'>1Co 15:58</a><br/> Preserves from evil<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=26'>Exo 15:26</a><br/> Leads to assured hope<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=6&verse=11'>Heb 6:11</a><br/> God rewards<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=11&verse=14'>Deu 11:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=6'>Heb 11:6</a><br/> In temporal matters leads to:<br/> - Favor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=11&verse=27'>Pro 11:27</a> <br/> - Prosperity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=10&verse=4'>Pro 10:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=13&verse=4'>Pro 13:4</a> <br/> - Honor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=12&verse=24'>Pro 12:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=22&verse=29'>Pro 22:29</a> <br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=6&verse=8'>Pro 6:8</a><br/> Exemplified:<br/> - Ruth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=2&verse=17'>Rth 2:17</a> <br/> - Hezekiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=21'>2Ch 31:21</a> <br/> - Nehemiah and his helpers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=6'>Neh 4:6</a> <br/> - Psalmist<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=119&verse=60'>Psa 119:60</a> <br/> - Apostles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=42'>Act 5:42</a> <br/> - Apollos<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=18&verse=25'>Act 18:25</a> <br/> - Titus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=8&verse=22'>2Co 8:22</a> <br/> - Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=2&verse=9'>1Th 2:9</a> <br/> - Onesiphorus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=1&verse=17'>2Ti 1:17</a><br/><a href='S:Industry'>Industry</a>; <a href='S:Zeal, Religious'>Zeal</a>; <a href='S:Idleness'>Idleness</a>; <a href='S:Slothfulness'>Slothfulness</a> "}]}